Configuration GitPod

Step 1 : Workspace GitPod
To open Gitpod you have to go to your github repository and put https://gitpod.io at the beginning of the URL of the git project URL.

Once the workspace is open, put all the folders and files of the plugin in a single folder if it is not already done.

Step 2: Installing DDEV
Install DDEV : brew install ddev/ddev/ddev
Configure DDEV as a WordPress project: ddev config --project-type=wordpress
Start DDEV : ddev start

Step 3 : Installing WordPress
Download WordPress : ddev wp core download
Put the extension under wp-content/plugins

Step 4 : Launch DDEV : ddev launch

Step 5 : Configure WordPress and then activate the add-on in the WordPress extension menu.
